Package: vrgti
Title: Convert VRT Mosaics to GDAL Tile Index (GTI)
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Michael", "Sumner", , "mdsumner@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-2471-7511"))
Description: Convert GDAL Virtual Raster (VRT) mosaic files to the GDAL Tile 
    Index (GTI) format. Parses VRT XML to extract tile source locations and 
    spatial footprints, validates that the VRT represents a simple mosaic 
    (SimpleSource only), and writes a GTI-compatible GeoPackage with layer 
    metadata. The resulting GTI datasource supports efficient spatial filtering 
    and scales to very large tile collections.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
